Class DefaultMultipartResourceRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.portlet.filter.RenderStateWrapper
      • javax.portlet.filter.PortletRequestWrapper
        • javax.portlet.filter.ClientDataRequestWrapper
          • javax.portlet.filter.ResourceRequestWrapper
            • com.liferay.portletmvc4spring.multipart.DefaultMultipartResourceRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MultipartResourceRequest, javax.portlet.ClientDataRequest, javax.portlet.PortletRequest, javax.portlet.RenderState, javax.portlet.ResourceRequest, MultipartRequest

    public class DefaultMultipartResourceRequest
extends javax.portlet.filter.ResourceRequestWrapper
implements MultipartResourceRequest
    Default implementation of the MultipartResourceRequest interface. Provides management of pre-generated parameter values.
    Since:
    5.1
    Author:
    Juergen Hoeller, Arjen Poutsma, Neil Griffin
    See Also:
    PortletMultipartResolver
